Paper: hep-th/9210112

Date: 1992-10-20

Title: Anyons on a Torus

Authors: Yutaka Hosotani and Choon-Lin Ho

Comments: 4 pages, plain TeX, UMN-TH-1116/92

We prove the equivalence between anyon quantum mechanics on a torus andChern-Simons gauge theory. It is also shown that the Hamiltonian and totalmomenta commute among themselves only in the physical Hilbert space.